Available Tools: get_temperature | get_humidity | get_wind_speed | get_uv_index
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "location": "string", "unit": "celsius|fahrenheit" }
Response Schema: { "value": number, "unit": "string", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: What is the current temperature in Tokyo?
Call: { "func_call": "get_temperature", "location": "Tokyo", "unit": "celsius" }
Response: { "value": 24.5, "unit": "celsius", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T14:30:00Z" }

Question: How hot is it right now in New York?
Call: { "func_call": "get_temperature", "location": "New York", "unit": "fahrenheit" }
Response: { "value": 68.2, "unit": "fahrenheit", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T09:15:00Z" }

Question: Give me the temperature in London in Celsius.
Call: { "func_call": "get_temperature", "location": "London", "unit": "celsius" }
